    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Accounts] AS [a]
        WHERE ([a].[Email] = @__Email_0) AND ([a].[Password] = @__Password_1)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Accounts] AS [a]
        WHERE ([a].[Email] = @__Email_0) AND ([a].[Password] = @__Password_1)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
